{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2252434_translations":{"at":1773942567645,"data":{"id":2252434,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"JYP엔터테인먼트 소속 5인조 걸그룹 ITZY의 메인보컬 멤버. 예지와 함께 그룹 맏언니이다. 팀 내 사랑과 평화를 담당하고 있다.","name":"리아","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Choi Ji-su (최지수; born July 21, 2000), known professionally as Lia (리아), is a South Korean singer under JYP Entertainment. She is a member of the South Korean girl group ITZY.","name":"Lia","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"崔智壽","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lia","primary":false}}]}},"person_1081493_translations":{"at":1773942572124,"data":{"id":1081493,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Helen Ma Hoi-Lun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"马海伦，邵氏演员。1960年开始参演多部邵氏电影。1970年加入佳艺电视，演出多套电视剧，如《红楼梦》、《仙鹤神针》、《鹿鼎记》、《神雕侠侣》、《雪山飞狐》等。1978年客串演出丽的电视《天龙诀》。1990年后加入无线电视，曾演出多套电视剧如《天涯歌女》，《真情》，《皆大欢喜》、《火舞黄沙》。","name":"马海伦","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"馬海倫，邵氏演員。1960 年開始參演多部邵氏電影。1970 年加入佳藝電視，演出多套電視劇，如《紅樓夢》、《仙鶴神針》、《鹿鼎記》、《神鵰俠侶》、《雪山飛狐》等。1978 年客串演出麗的電視《天龍訣》。1990 年後加入無線電視，曾演出多套電視劇如《天涯歌女》，《真情》，《皆大歡喜》、《火舞黃沙》。","name":"馬海倫","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Helen Ma","primary":false}}]}},"person_3954423_translations":{"at":1773942579459,"data":{"id":3954423,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mariana Calderón","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mariana Calderón","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1322692_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773942598696,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/66goUG18qJdtbnJ7R4HIsibUMKI.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"},{"id":36,"name":"Phim Lịch Sử"}],"homepage":"","id":1322692,"imdb_id":"tt33093531","origin_country":["IE","GB"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Saipan","overview":"","popularity":1.4837,"poster_path":"/s7IbZFANLHKNglQ9IfjDdrHCVNZ.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":11667,"logo_path":"/dhBJdstAolGmqRfbQfElhsU1cTo.png","name":"Northern Ireland Screen","origin_country":"GB"},{"id":1898,"logo_path":"/8ix6SGlJiyuUDxLBtY8E0PY2G7w.png","name":"Fís Éireann/Screen Ireland","origin_country":"IE"},{"id":129815,"logo_path":"/qbCmnVTQEuFqrVkbxn3i9P7Jrcw.png","name":"Wild Atlantic Pictures","origin_country":"IE"},{"id":80995,"logo_path":"/awknjEFU2v2qRKAOe1MZkaMDYN2.png","name":"Fine Point Films","origin_country":"GB"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"IE","name":"Ireland"},{"iso_3166_1":"GB","name":"United Kingdom"}],"release_date":"2025-11-08","revenue":0,"runtime":91,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Saipan","video":false,"vote_average":6,"vote_count":5}},"person_70690_translations":{"at":1773942601885,"data":{"id":70690,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kenneth Lo Wai-Kwong (Chinese: 盧惠光) is a Hong Kong actor, martial artist, and stuntman. He was a member of the Jackie Chan Stunt Team.","name":"Ken Lo Wai-Kwong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"노혜광","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　卢惠光于1959年3月17日出生于泰国，是一名泰国华侨，也曾经是一位泰拳冠军（香港泰拳比赛七连冠）。上世纪80年代进入香港影坛。曾出演过徐克执导的《打工皇帝》。虽是几分钟的镜头，共拍了三天，但从那时起卢惠光才发现自己有喜欢拍电影的感觉。于是就兼职拍拍电影。他1986年开始正式为成龙的“威禾”影业拍摄第一部影片《扭计杂牌军》，这是一部成家班成员共同演出的电影，由钱升玮指导，成龙本人也在影片开始时有客串表演。后来他又演过李修贤的两部作品《皇家饭》和《霹雳先锋》，卢惠光开始进入成家班的时候，基本都是在配角的边缘徘徊。直到1994年卢惠光出演《醉拳2》才开始技惊四座一举成名，继而成为成龙的死党兼保镖。黎强权时代的“空中三连踢”，卢惠光时代的“一字马”都可以说是成家班在不同时代的典范表现，这也是成家班的实力和创造力的完美体现。他还参拍电影《宝贝计划》、《新警察故事》、《少年阿虎》、《雷霆战警》、《尖峰时刻》、《醉拳2》以及电视剧《斗鱼》。","name":"卢惠光","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"盧惠光於 1959 年 3 月 17 日出生於泰國，是一名泰國華僑，也曾經是一位泰拳冠軍（香港泰拳比賽七聯冠）。上世紀 80 年代進入香港影壇。曾出演過徐克執導的《打工皇帝》。雖是幾分鐘的鏡頭，共拍了三天，但從那時起盧惠光才發現自己有喜歡拍電影的感覺。於是就兼職拍拍電影。他 1986 年開始正式為成龍的“威禾”影業拍攝第一部影片《扭計雜牌軍》，這是一部成家班成員共同演出的電影，由錢升瑋指導，成龍本人也在影片開始時有客串表演。後來他又演過李修賢的兩部作品《皇家飯》和《霹靂先鋒》，盧惠光開始進入成家班的時候，基本都是在配角的邊緣徘徊。直到 1994 年盧惠光出演《醉拳 2》才開始技驚四座一舉成名，繼而成為成龍的死黨兼保鏢。黎強權時代的“空中三聯踢”，盧惠光時代的“一字馬”都可以説是成家班在不同時代的典範表現，這也是成家班的實力和創造力的完美體現。他還參拍電影《寶貝計劃》、《新警察故事》、《少年阿虎》、《雷霆戰警》、《火拼時速》、《醉拳 2》以及電視劇《鬥魚》。","name":"盧惠光","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"盧惠光","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lô Huệ Quang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кен Ло","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ken Lo Wai-Kwong","primary":false}}]}},"person_6045937_translations":{"at":1773942605533,"data":{"id":6045937,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wu Younan","primary":false}}]}},"tv_314924_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773942610894,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/sINi0J617COomOq5lVz9IG98B1k.jpg","created_by":[],"episode_ru